title: Chicago man gets 12 years for role in Cleveland drug ring
text:
Chicago man gets 12 years for role in Cleveland drug ring 
Published By: Cleveland.com - Today 
A Chicago man was sentenced Friday to 12 years and one month in prison for his role in a large-scale cocaine and heroin ring in Cleveland....
